>
<h2 id="supplies">School Supplies</h2><p><strong>书 (shū)</strong> book, <strong>笔 (bǐ)</strong> pen, <strong>纸 (zhǐ)</strong> paper, <strong>本子 (běnzi)</strong> notebook, <strong>字典 (zìdiǎn)</strong> dictionary, <strong>书包 (shūbāo)</strong> backpack.</p>
    <h2 id="phrases">Classroom Phrases</h2><p><strong>听不懂 (tīng bù dǒng)</strong> I don't understand (listening). <strong>请再说一遍 (qǐng zài shuō yī biàn)</strong> Please say it again. <strong>这个怎么说？(zhège zěnme shuō?)</strong> How do you say this?</p>
    <h2 id="subjects">School Subjects</h2><p><strong>数学 (shùxué)</strong> math, <strong>中文 (zhōngwén)</strong> Chinese, <strong>英语 (yīngyǔ)</strong> English, <strong>历史 (lìshǐ)</strong> history, <strong>科学 (kēxué)</strong> science. Browse more vocabulary in our <a href="/chinese/tools/hsk-vocabulary/">HSK Vocabulary Browser</a>.</p>
</BlogLayout>
